              "type": "spell",
              "url": "https://www.wowhead.com/tbc/spell=13819/summon-warhorse"
            }
          ],
          "level_range": "6",
          "section": "Leveling Tips for Holy Paladin Healer in TBC Classic",
          "source_links": [
            {
              "href": "https://www.wowhead.com/tbc/spell=498/divine-protection",
              "text": "Divine Protection"
            },
            {
              "href": "https://www.wowhead.com/tbc/spell=7328/redemption",
              "text": "Redemption"
            },
            {
              "href": "https://www.wowhead.com/tbc/spell=19750/flash-of-light",
              "text": "Flash of Light"
            },
            {
              "href": "https://www.wowhead.com/tbc/spell=635",
              "text": ""
            },
            {
              "href": "https://www.wowhead.com/tbc/spell=13819/summon-warhorse",
              "text": "Summon Warhorse"
            }
          ],
          "text": "There are a few \"milestone\" spells worth picking up as you level. At level 6, you can train Divine Protection , which is your first in the line of \"bubbles\", rendering you invulnerable for a short period. At level 12, there is a quest available to obtain Redemption , your resurrection spell. At level 20, you can train Flash of Light , which is a quicker, smaller heal compared to . At level 40, you get a quest to obtain a free mount, Summon Warhorse !"
        }
      ],
      "heading": "Leveling Tips for Holy Paladin Healer in TBC Classic"
    }
